OL,3,CKemi Badenoch brands inheritance tax
OL,4,Cchange 'immoral' as she visits NI farm
OL,6,FKemi Badenoch has branded Government
OL,7,Fchanges to inheritance tax for farmers
OL,8,F"immoral" as she made her first visit
OL,9,Fto Northern Ireland since becoming
OL,10,FConservative Party leader.
OL,12,FMs Badenoch visited a farm in Co Down
OL,13,Fas she vowed to do everything she
OL,14,Fcould to fight the "family farms tax".
OL,16,FFrom April 2026, inherited
OL,17,Fagricultural assets worth more than #1
OL,18,Fmillion, which were previously exempt,
OL,19,Fwill have to pay inheritance tax at
OL,20,F20%.
