OL,3,CKemi Badenoch brands inheritance tax
OL,4,Cchange 'immoral' as she visits NI farm
OL,6,FThe move has been controversial across
OL,7,Fthe UK, and has been widely criticised
OL,8,Fby political parties and farmers in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, which is heavily
OL,10,Freliant on agriculture.
OL,12,FMs Badenoch met members of the Jackson
OL,13,Ffamily as she visited the Fairview
OL,14,Fdairy farm near Bangor in Co Down.
OL,16,FThe Tory leader fed some calves as she
OL,17,Fwas shown around the farm grounds.
