OL,3,CKemi Badenoch brands inheritance tax
OL,4,Cchange 'immoral' as she visits NI farm
OL,6,FAsked about the reaction of Northern
OL,7,FIreland farmers to changes in
OL,8,Finheritance tax, Ms Badenoch said:
OL,9,F"The family farms tax is an immoral
OL,10,Ftax.
OL,12,F"We know how difficult farming is and
OL,13,Fthe Conservative Party will reverse
OL,14,Fthis as soon as we get the opportunity.
OL,16,F"We are trying to get the Labour
OL,17,FGovernment to do so.
OL,19,F"We want farmers to know that we are
OL,20,Fwith you, we understand."
