OL,3,CKemi Badenoch brands inheritance tax
OL,4,Cchange 'immoral' as she visits NI farm
OL,6,FThe Conservative leader said farming
OL,7,Fneeds a lot of assets but often does
OL,8,Fnot give huge returns.
OL,10,FShe added: "Taxing those assets to
OL,11,Fforce farmers to often give up their
OL,12,Fland and their children or their
OL,13,Fgrandchildren to not continue in this
OL,14,Fway of life, I believe, is immoral.
OL,16,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,17,Ffight the family farms tax."
OL,19,FThe Fairview farm had previously been
OL,20,Fvisited by Theresa May when she was
OL,21,Fprime minister in 2018.
