OL,6,FThey took the step after a
OL,7,Frecommendation from the The
OL,8,FIndependent Reporting Commission (IRC)
OL,9,Fwhich said a "twin-track" process of
OL,10,Flaw enforcement and tackling the roots
OL,11,Fof paramilitarism is needed.
OL,13,FMs Badenoch said: "We looked at this
OL,14,Fproposal when we were in government.
OL,16,F"We didn't bring it forward because
OL,17,Fone of the things we must remember is
OL,18,Fthere is no space for paramilitary
OL,19,Forganisations.
